Title: Hide "Update DNS Cache" according to current settings
Level: 1
Component: wato
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.6.0p23
Date: 1616075747
Class: fix

The button "Update DNS Cache" under a host settings was always visible and therfore ignoring the site specific global setting "Use DNS lookup cache".
It's now not shown anymore if the DNS Cache is not used.
